<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/'}) %>

<div class = "container mx-auto px-4">
  <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-1g p-6">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
        <p class="py-6">Build something new today with Lego!</p>
        <a href="/lego/sets" class="btn btn-primary">Join the fun</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/002-1.jpg" alt="4.5V Samsonite Gears Motor Set" />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">4.5V Samsonite Gears Motor Set</h2>
          <p>This set was released in America (USA/CAN) by Samsonite in 1965. 
            It was never released in Europe.
          </p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/002-1" class="btn btn-primary">VIEW</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/010423-1.jpg" alt="The Majestic Horse" />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">The Majestic Horse</h2>
          <p>Designed by previous 2017 Lego Masters UK winners Nathan Dias and Steve Guinness.
            Given to select members of the Recognised Lego Fan Media group for an April fools prank 
            in 2023, only around 10 are known to exist.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/010423-1" class="btn btn-primary">VIEW</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img class="w-full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/0241357594-1.jpg" alt="Star Wars Book Set" />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Star Wars: Build Your Own Adventure: Galactic Missions</h2>
          <p>Published by DK Children (Dorling Kindersley) as a hardcover released on August 1, 2019 
            in the United Kingdom and on August 6, 2019 in the United States. 
            The book contains 80 pages.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/lego/sets/0241357594-1" class="btn btn-primary">VIEW</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>